      "title": "feat(masses): Add church and neighborhood to mass dates\n\nIntroduces new fields `eglise` and `quartier` to the `MassDate` type to store location details for commemorative masses. This enhancement allows for more precise tracking and display of mass information within the application. Additionally, the `saveMassRequest` function in `services/db.ts` has been updated to accept and save these new location details, ensuring data integrity and completeness for each scheduled mass. The `App.tsx` component has also been refactored to manage and display these new church information fields.",
